high_descs: Move to the stove on the right.
Pick up the dirty pan on the stove.
Turn right, bring the pan to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned pan to the cabinet on the left, right of the stove.
Put the cleaned pan in the cabinet right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan in a cabinet right of the stove.

high_descs: Take a step to your right so you're in front of the stove then walk to the stove.
Pick up the dirty frying pan that's in front of you on the back left burner.
Turn right and take a step to your right then walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and take a tiny step forward then turn right and take a tiny step forward then turn right.
Open the cupboards to the right of the stove then put the pan down there before closing the doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in the cupboard.

high_descs: Go to the cabinet to the right of the stove
Put the pan in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in the kitchen cabinet
